# Frontend workspace env vars (Phase 0 has none required).
#
# Vite exposes only variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser bundle.
# Server-only secrets must never live in this file.

# Optional: override the OpenEMR webroot used by oeFetch when developing
# against a non-default install path. Most users do not need this.
# VITE_OPENEMR_WEBROOT=/openemr
